{"tid":49604,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"諾基亞控告蘋果侵犯32項專利　新一波專利戰來襲","createTime":"2016-12-21T23:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-05T23:13:49.000Z","uid":25125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b977e91c4dd1bdf31fcd421f90c667031231cc7","tid":49604,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:47:01.000Z","msg":"諾基亞控告蘋果侵犯32項專利　新一波專利戰來襲<br />\n2016年12月22日04:50<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161222/640_ad0a9a36ebde339a7c0248a023998462.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161222%2F640_ad0a9a36ebde339a7c0248a023998462.jpg&h=a6ee3611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諾基亞已在德國與美國多地控告蘋果專利侵權，蘋果與三星間延燒多年的專利戰才剛要偃旗息鼓，馬上又捲入新一波專利糾紛。路透<br />\n<br />\n蘋果（Apple）和三星多年專利訴訟才偃旗息鼓，新一波專利戰恐怕又將到來！<br />\n近年轉戰電信設備領域的芬蘭科技廠諾基亞（NOKIA）周三宣布，已在美國和歐洲對蘋果提出告訴，指控蘋果侵害諾基亞所持有的32項專利，稱先前已與蘋果為此協商「數年之久」，最終決定「採取行動」。<br />\n諾基亞已在德國杜塞道夫（Dusseldorf）、曼海姆（Mannheim）、慕尼黑等地以及美國德州東區地方法院，向蘋果提出專利侵權告訴，並表示2011年雖與蘋果達成部分專利授權協議，但諾基亞後來所取得的創新專利也被蘋果許多產品採用，蘋果卻拒絕了諾基亞進一步提出的授權合約。<br />\n諾基亞指控蘋果侵犯的32項專利，遍及「面板、使用者介面、軟體、天線、晶片組及視訊編碼」等方面，包括iPhone和iPad均採用了未經諾基亞授權的專利。諾基亞據稱將在更多地區向蘋果提出專利侵權訴訟。<br />\n諾基亞除了自有專利，2013年收購與西門子合資企業Nokia Siemens Networks（NSN）及今年收購法國阿爾卡特朗訊（Alcatel-Lucent）後，也取得重要智慧財產權組合資產。（劉利貞／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/finance/20161222/1017925/%E8%AB%BE%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%9E%E6%8E%A7%E5%91%8A%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E4%BE%B5%E7%8A%AF32%E9%A0%85%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9%E3%80%80%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%80%E6%B3%A2%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9%E6%88%B0%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Ffinance%2F20161222%2F1017925%2F%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E5%259F%25BA%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E7%258A%25AF32%25E9%25A0%2585%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2588%25B0%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25A5%25B2&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANngT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=30b45b4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/finance/20161222/1017925/%E8%AB%BE%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%9E%E6%8E%A7%E5%91%8A%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E4%BE%B5%E7%8A%AF32%E9%A0%85%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9%E3%80%80%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%80%E6%B3%A2%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9%E6%88%B0%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%B2</a><br />\n<br />\nNokia淨係靠嗰堆專利都夠玩多幾十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a76cdc5f58ae9332dea81496c6b8ba18fb1169","tid":49604,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:08:08.000Z","msg":"nokia咁積極咬apole即係佢真田係回歸手機市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nnokia一出an旗艦即狗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5dd0f396d5b64082c97e741418bb037f6c3c8e","tid":49604,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:18:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>nokia咁積極咬apole即係佢真田係回歸手機市場&lt;img src=&quot;lihkg_android_asset/faces/normal/tongue.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;<br />\nnokia一出an旗艦即狗衝&lt;img src=&quot;lihkg_android_asset/faces/normal/agree.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n陣間揾間大陸廠做貼牌機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad3f807b88f13df3af0be79dfcc54720b69244f","tid":49604,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>nokia咁積極咬apole即係佢真田係回歸手機市場&lt;img src=&quot;lihkg_android_asset/faces/normal/tongue.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;<br />\nnokia一出an旗艦即狗衝&lt;img src=&quot;lihkg_android_asset/faces/normal/agree.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n陣間揾間大陸廠做貼牌機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif