$oik9f9&amp;&amp;4U0XXsfdEeaAzApYClQBIQ$$</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係nokia mobile嘅新網頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nokia.com/en_int/phones\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nokia.com%2Fen_int%2Fphones&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANngT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=1e091f88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nokia.com/en_int/phones</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會有Pure View , 因為賣斷左﹙定授權未過期﹚MS，Nokia 理論上要由零再開始相機研發。"},{"pid":"6a0735efe403051f26e624dab9c30a0cbdabe5d1","tid":49604,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T19:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有錢打咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNokia 大撚把錢啦，手機業務剩係食專利一定唔會執，同埋佢係芬蘭最大財團，咩生意都有撈。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好僟好多人都唔知nokia係電信設備大佬黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢食左西門子同阿爾卡特-朗訊，加埋自己手上堆專利，好屈機架。"},{"pid":"6bc500f2a288d192ae128904e393cc2650cb89aa","tid":49604,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T19:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有錢打咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNokia 大撚把錢啦，手機業務剩係食專利一定唔會執，同埋佢係芬蘭最大財團，咩生意都有撈。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好僟好多人都唔知nokia係電信設備大佬黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD人仲以為motorola 淨係出電話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMoto 仲係營運緊GPS ，係美軍公司﹙Motorola Solution，俾人拆骨係 Motorola Mobility﹚"}]}